content.rendered:
Directed by Ashwini Chaudhary.

Written by Ashwini Chaudhary. Vikash Mani. Ahmed Siraj. Ahmed Siraj.

Cast Shreyas Talpade(Apurva). Aftab Shivdasani(Aditya). Sonnalli Seygall(Isha). Ishita Dutta(Prerana). Pawan Malhotra(Bhaiya Ji). Vijay Raaz(Nizam). Manu Rishi Chadha(Balam). Anil Charanjeett(Dibankar). Pankaj Jha(Kesariya). Jameel Khan(Ansari). Niharika Kundu(Riya). Tanuka Laghate(Aparna). Venus Singh(Aarushi). Neeraj Sood(Bhanu) . Siddharth Bhardwaj(Nila Babu (as Siddharth Bharadwaj)). Sidharth Bhardwaj(Nila babu). Samir Chandra(Government Officer). Yusof Mutahar(Rahul). Bhupesh Pandya(Murli). Utkarsh Singh(Babloo Sharma). Rahul Tanwar(Kedar). Sambhav Jain(Ramesh Shetty (uncredited))

Language Hindi.

Producers Abhishek Ankur. Narendra Hirawat. Aman Kumar. Vikash Mani. Zafar Mehdi. Ajay Sharma.

Production Lovely Films. NH Studios.
